title: (BONUS EP) Wisconsin Crimes
description: This month, the gals tread lightly in enemy territory. Topics include a fiery streak of destruction, a pretty badass political speech, and a very obvious flag. Grab some Door Peninsula Winery Cranbernet, set your badger traps, and tune in for Wisconsin Crimes.  For a full list of show sponsors, visit: https://wineandcrimepodcast.com/sponsors/
